text: Honson Chin (born 12 January 1956) is a former Jamaican cyclist. He competed in the sprint and tandem events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Jamaican male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Jamaica Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
